        "created_at": "2023-09-26T14:02:04.063Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I do address on the premox subject in the antepenultimate paragraph of the article.</p>\n<p>Given their work on dissolved oxygen at bottling, sulfite levels during \u00e9levage and at bottling, cork selection and analysis, they are certainly working hard on it. Of course, natural cork is natural cork\u2026</p>",
